org.shared.parallel

Interface TraversalPolicy<V extends Traversable<V,E>,E extends Edge<V>>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the node type.
    E - the edge type.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LimitedMemoryPolicy

    public interface TraversalPolicy<V extends Traversable<V,E>,E extends Edge<V>>
    Defines a total ordering and depth assignment to a collection of Traversables via Traversable.setOrder(int) and Traversable.setDepth(int). The modifications serve as a hint to Engine and do not affect the correctness of the calculation.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      int assign(V root)
      Makes a total ordering and depth assignment to all nodes reachable from the given node.
